org.sql: SELECT projects.* FROM projects WHERE projects.status = "$1" AND projects.id IN (SELECT em.project_id FROM enabled_modules AS em WHERE em.name = 'repository') AND projects.identifier = "$2" LIMIT "$3"

rewrites.sql: SELECT projects.* FROM projects WHERE projects.status = "$1" AND projects.id IN (SELECT em.project_id FROM enabled_modules AS em WHERE em.name = 'repository' LIMIT 1) AND projects.identifier = "$2" LIMIT "$3"
